You can simply ask Alexa to control your iHelios Living Reinvented devices. After connecting Alexa to your products in a few simple steps:
(1) Download our Living Reinvented app in app market then register an account;
(2) Configure our devices in our Living Reinvented app and change appropriate name for your devices;
(3) Search Living reinvented skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(4) Enable Living Reinvented skill, and you'll be navigated to Living Reinvented login page;
(5) Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
(6) Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on the bedroom light”
“Alexa, turn off the bedroom light”
“Alexa, set the bedroom light to 50%”
“Alexa, brighten the bedroom light to 50%”
“Alexa, dim the bedroom light to 50%”
"Alexa, set bedroom light to green"
